    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone looking for utility over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some typical age-related wear such as minor fluid seeps and a less-than-perfect idle. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, small dings, and some paint fading, while the interior shows clear signs of use with some staining and wear on the upholstery. It has been maintained well enough to stay on the road, but a buyer should expect to invest in some minor repairs or cosmetic touch-ups down the line.",
